@startuml
title BP-08 - Payment Product Configuration

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Open payment product configuration;
:Choose payment policy;
:Input product code, name, price and status;
:Input revenue account code and name;

|Platform|
:Read TenantID from JWT context;
:Validate payment policy belongs to tenant;
:Validate product code unique within tenant;
:Validate price is greater than zero;
:Validate revenue account fields if supplied;

if (Validation passed?) then (Yes)
  :Create or update PaymentProduct;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Finance Officer|
:Product becomes available for bill generation;
stop

note right
Current endpoints:
- POST /payment-products
- GET /payment-products
- GET /payment-products/{id}
- PUT /payment-products/{id}
Legacy singular routes are also available.
end note
@enduml
